_sText:
This is an adaptation of a mip called gg_skyward. It doesnt  look anything like the original at this point and i am not continuing on this project. there are light effects and custom wall panels. light environment, and volumetric fog. there are killzones(trigger_hurt) and 2 spawns. 32 start points for the entire map.



Its got the light emitting textures and i have added the lights.rad file to accompany this mip.
